{
  "_doc": [
    "Point-of-interest registry consumed by scripts/worldgen/poi_placement.gd.",
    "placement.mode:",
    "  'cell'   one POI per cellChunks x cellChunks region of chunks, at a",
    "           seed-jittered chunk (optionally gated by 'chance' 0..1);",
    "  'zone'   one per Voronoi level zone, in the zone's center chunk;",
    "  'chance' independent per-chunk roll.",
    "biomes: optional whitelist (omit = any land biome). minTier: minimum zone",
    "level requirement for the POI to appear.",
    "parts: entities placed around the anchor tile. dx/dy are tile offsets.",
    "  kind     sprite kind drawn by WorldEntity (see world_entity.gd);",
    "  station  opens that station on click (bank/shop/recipes -- ids must match",
    "           skill_sites.json 'stations');",
    "  hook     placeholder feature: click prints the hook message (used for",
    "           skills with no sim yet, e.g. thieving/tracking);",
    "  boss     part is the zone-tier boss enemy anchor.",
    "  enemy    a specific named GUARDIAN from enemies.json (e.g. 'Skeletons') that",
    "           holds this set-piece; aggressive by default. Its own level/drops apply,",
    "           so 'minTier' just gates the POI into a zone where that level fits.",
    "safe: no monsters spawn in this chunk; respawn: player respawns here on",
    "death. clusterSites: N same-node gather sites ring the anchor (depots).",
    "To add a POI type: append an entry here and reuse existing part kinds (or",
    "add a draw kind in world_entity.gd/iso_sprites.gd for new art)."
  ],
